Package: remap
Type: Package
Title: Regional Spatial Modeling with Continuous Borders
Version: 0.1.1.9004
Authors@R: person("Jadon", "Wagstaff", email = "jadonw@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates separate regression models for different spatial regions. If regional 
    models are continuous, the resulting prediction surface is continuous across the spatial 
    dimensions, even at region borders.
